name: Wookiee Guide (V)
Lore: 'Chewie felt right at home in the forests of Endor, which closely resemble the environment on his homeworld of Kashyyyk.',
Text: 'Stack a Wookiee from your Lost Pile on Grrrghrrrgh!. OR Deploy a Wookiee stacked on Grrrghrrrgh! to Kashyyyk (as if from hand). OR Once per game, draw X cards from top of Reserve Deck, where X = number of cards stacked on Grrrghrrrgh!.',
